items.title: Self Branding
items.headline: An Approach to Renew Yourself In 'New Normal'
objectives_summary: Today in this New Normal, things are changing rapidly. What is required today is to project yourself as a Brand. This is the only way one can keep himself/herself ready to face pandemic like crisis in future too. Professionals sometimes wonder that they despite of being so intellectual and efficient, still do not get due appreciation and recognition. Actually, they don’t know how to Translate their ‘Efficiency’ in to ‘Effectiveness’. This ‘Effectiveness’ is the pivot of this module. Organizations are not interested in what you are? They are interested to know What you can do and how effectively can you do prove your worth.
